```plantuml
@startuml dylanvanh_MunchOut

actor Customer
actor Restaurant
participant "Flutter Frontend" as Flutter
participant "Flask Backend" as Flask
participant "Database" as DB

Customer -> Flutter: Browse Events
Flutter -> Flask: GET /api/events
Flask -> DB: Query Events
DB --> Flask: Events Data
Flask --> Flutter: JSON Response
Flutter --> Customer: Display Events

Customer -> Flutter: Book Event (EventID)
Flutter -> Flask: POST /api/bookings {EventID, CustomerID}
Flask -> DB: Create Booking
DB --> Flask: Booking Confirmation
Flask --> Flutter: Booking Success
Flutter --> Customer: Booking Confirmation

Restaurant -> Flutter: Login (Credentials)
Flutter -> Flask: POST /api/auth/login {Credentials}
Flask -> DB: Validate Credentials
DB --> Flask: Auth Token
Flask --> Flutter: Auth Response
Flutter --> Restaurant: Dashboard Access

Restaurant -> Flutter: Create Event (EventDetails)
Flutter -> Flask: POST /api/events {EventDetails}
Flask -> DB: Store Event
DB --> Flask: Event ID
Flask --> Flutter: Event Created
Flutter --> Restaurant: Event Confirmation

@enduml
```